title: Uvi Workstation 2.5.16 Windows
description:
This is the official installer for UVI Workstation 2.5.16 32 and 64 bits for Windows. This is the last version that support RTAS for Pro Tools.

For Exmaple, if you have Pro Tools 9 MP, you can`t install the latest UVI version, you have to stay with 2.5.16 because PT 9MP need RTAS and it was discontinued in the newer versions.

This is NOT cracked, It's just the official installer, it's harder to find
